<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RADDatabase<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>compact<sp/>SQLite<sp/>wrapper<sp/>for<sp/>application<sp/>data,<sp/>settings,</highlight></codeline>
